data.eml:eml: Revision of the New World species of (Hymenoptera: Ichneumonidae: Sisyrostolinae), with a key to the world species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Bennett, Andrew M. R., Sääksjärvi, Ilari E., Broad, Gavin R. (2013): Revision of the New World species of (Hymenoptera: Ichneumonidae: Sisyrostolinae), with a key to the world species. Zootaxa 3702 (5): 425-436, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3702.5.2
